Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4月份 昂魔法學院迎接著新生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問詢處在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領了學生卡的同學請去體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽是這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和五十島被委託在入學式幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是如出一轍呢 這裡和我們生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我家的妹妹也請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是編入初等部的伊田二葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊田的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:15.20,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1047,642)\blur1\fad(450,450)}巫師氣息的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是一三的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這個可怕的阿姨是五十島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是阿姨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吐槽可怕這個詞沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來承蒙你們關照我家的一三了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才是承蒙關照 我是七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是受了不少關照呢 我叫五十島胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是伊田一三的妹妹 二葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道其實沒有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者只有伊田是從橋下撿來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是如假包換的我的妹妹啊 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛也沒辦法啊 誰讓她是我撫養大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是世界第一可愛 宇宙第一的好女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一三是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼 為什麼說我是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 二葉為什麼會變成魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個和二葉同班的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春假有那個男孩的生日party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生只有二葉被邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我勸她不要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二葉非不聽話一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸變成兄妹吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果氣過頭一不小心用了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 冒失燒掉了二葉的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那個的影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 一三不要再說那種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二葉 等下啊 不要走那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個都好有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光… 為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問我為什麼 當然是因為我也變成魔法使了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才問你為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後會解釋的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去參加入學式 回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果一直沒有從月光那裡聽到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣時間不知不覺地流逝著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天 意想不到的事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你撮下背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…月光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不這樣的話 和武很難搭上話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也有自我反省
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止對武做了好多過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受傷後 自己的身體變得不聽使喚 心情很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道不是武的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是沒有發洩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點晚了 可我想好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直想著應該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武 你果然不會再原諒我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會原諒我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們和好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我們和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的春天 溫暖蓬勃的氣氛中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處處充滿了希望與喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光 擦擦汗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 武
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六 白色情人節有收到七瀨的回禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 和哥哥沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只屬於兩個人的秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我比收到誰的禮物比較開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安 維歐莉特老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一氏老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是和五十島同學一起吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有伊田的妹妹和我的弟弟月光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 大家兄弟們融洽地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七瀨同學 你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.30,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能和你的想法會非常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給弟弟當個好模範 為他指引方向可能會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課的時候不要來偷看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去看看我可愛妹妹大顯身手的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊田 不好好練習的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就會被二葉超過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤魚看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小武
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武 饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快向我償罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搶我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡桃 還有薄暮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這回輪到我奪走你的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鷲津 你怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌 我想動手的話早得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微想聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊天… 找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你讓堂歷史課
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然學校也有教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我的內容稍微有點不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在八世紀末
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法使被魔法使所統治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個統治階層的魔法使是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫師氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫害的歷史 在不同時代不斷重演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 我再也不用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一生都不會再使用第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以請放過我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要獨佔魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你們才是與眾不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巫師氣息的人就可以用魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個世上 只有我們才被允許使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這等貨色不配用魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法是高貴者才可以擁有的 神的恩賜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫師氣息干的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 與一部分人勾結 迫害弱小魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,課上沒教過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的話是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的直覺迴避的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 話說你知道龍泉寺和馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們亡靈引路人的頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是和我一起學習魔法的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫師氣息把力量強大而且能力特殊的和馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看作重要的戰鬥力 非常想他入伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你不加入巫師氣息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被邀請了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對加入好 多難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想加入啊 不過是考得上才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的能力的話 一定能當幹部候選人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以加入精英行列的話要當仁不讓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們想要的只是當做戰爭道具的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的魔法是我自已的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用途徑也要自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 巫師氣息怎容這種事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和馬同學 你不加入我們巫師氣息的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會產生很多問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些關我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力如果只為個人使用會是相當危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你們來指導我 任聽你們擺佈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其當殺人的道具 還不如死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如死了嗎 這真是太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是希望你活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母也是從心底希望你可以加入巫師氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是兒子的話 實現父母的願望是孝義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對他們做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是遵從規約的正規聯盟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在馬上放了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該先締結契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文件已經備齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋日 在遲來晨曦的映射下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不考慮做出這種事後 你的父母會怎麼樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聆聽鎮魂的樂響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.40,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,657)}Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 和馬的雙親被殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和馬他啊 對充滿對權利與金錢渴求的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傲慢的巫師氣息忍無可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且為了救濟與自己有相似經歷的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而創立了亡靈引路人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救濟？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前聽說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍泉寺和馬殺害了大量的魔法使和普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是真的 他確實殺了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 那些傢伙殺害的人數是和馬的數百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是持續千年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和馬想為這一切畫上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十世紀的末期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:16:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在東京 爆發了第一次魔法大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全給我殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和馬的一聲令下 戰爭爆發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲壯至極的戰鬥就要結束之時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快逃 陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七瀨陽子 當時還是千木陽子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我們的魔法老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫師氣息有十五位偉大的魔法使 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五位偉大的魔法使聯合力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把世界一分為二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和馬的左膀右臂 同時也是好朋友的籐川月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千木陽子勾引 而背叛了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後為了保護陽子而犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是和馬親手殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和馬是什麼心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼… 為什麼要告訴我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想邀請你加入引路人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要加入引路人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那至少可以把那把劍還回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把劍是月臣的遺物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月臣那個笨蛋 從心底深愛著陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才存在薄暮這個證據
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這把劍 絕不會把永遠讓給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也不要 那也不行 道理說不通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些事與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種人會第一個被當靶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你已經是魔法使了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇吧 現在馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引路人還是巫師氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法直接喊出加入巫師氣息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你還有救 我會等著的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你也會親自找上我們門來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙的本質最終會在你的直覺迴避下暴露無遺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去確認下吧 找四條桃花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 學院長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 七瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學院長在之前的大戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以巫師氣息的魔法使之身份參戰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母親 也是巫師氣息的魔法使之事屬實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 從哪聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那殺了龍泉寺和馬雙親的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個男人鼓吹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說見識過巫師氣息的黑暗歷史的冰山一角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可說引路人就是對的 這種判斷也很武斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後要選擇的還是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看能忍什麼到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是目白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V 你過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 這是眼淚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道已經醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺醒是階段性的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在強行喚醒也只會再度沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:22:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的占卜中 和馬大人的真正的覺醒之日不是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是X之日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我是魔女子·魔法子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是逃過腰斬一劫 迎來了第8集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止的道路非常凶險
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴滿的行程表和不規律的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時甚至還會在下集預告的演說中突然昏倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的我遇到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個昴之綠園牌青汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.73,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了這個之後 體質大為改善
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:06.74,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1019,106)\fad(1200,250)}昴之綠園牌青汁的粉絲心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(1019,265)\fad(1200,250)}純屬個人見解 毫無任何效果和療效
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不苦 容易入口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還富含一天所需的營養成分 大力推薦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.99,0:24:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是下一集也要邊吃飯邊喝昴之綠園牌青汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:09.77,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\fs50\c&HFFA862&\blur2\pos(288,596)}邁向崩壞的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OOH YEAH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They bring me DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,all the world is stereotypical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They're Playing out rules
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but act another,look
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now you thought you had me by the upper-hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I see through the face you've covered cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( FOUR )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,unleash the beast to fight inside at you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( THREE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To calm the fire that burns in front of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( TWO )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Without the fear and tears surrounding you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because your soul is what you were BORN TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,たとえ今まで生きる(strategy) 夢失っても　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(It's time now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:23:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ハンドルを切って 暴れる夢のまますっすっ進め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬のない人生に挑むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍もない感情を抱くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覚悟決めて行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自分自身をbreak away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全てを奪われる運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何を信じて生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ask yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the way there's nothing to live or die for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囲いも傷も恐れるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来さえも捨てるのはもんの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The choice is yours to make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is what I choose to live for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OOH YEAH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們令我無比失落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個世界都陳規蹈矩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在玩弄規則
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻演繹著另一個身份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在看起來 你自認為佔了我的上風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我卻看穿 那只是你用來掩蓋憤世嫉俗的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( FOUR )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放蕩不羈的獸性在你內心爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( THREE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰清冷靜的火燃在你表面燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( TWO )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不再被恐懼和淚水所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你的靈魂 與生俱有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你至今的人生戰略使夢想盡失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(正是時機)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:23:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索性改變方向 沿著現在這狂蕩的夢想繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要挑戰沒有嚴冬的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果懷有難以抑馭的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就做好覺悟勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把自己的身心解放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果注定是一切都被掠奪的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該以何信仰繼續生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捫心自問
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有什麼值得活著或是獻身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果侷限與傷害都令人恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就連未來也都丟棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你該作的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我選擇的生存之道
